&gt;&gt; Dr. Michael Chorost:
Shush [laughter]?

00:20:28.410 --> 00:20:31.090
Well, if you listen to it, you can
actually kind of hear that shush.

00:20:31.090 --> 00:20:32.860
Let me play that again.

00:20:32.860 --> 00:20:33.850
That's a finer pointer.

00:20:33.850 --> 00:20:36.290
It always gets lost on this slide.

