&gt;&gt; [Sound recording]
I like to play tennis.

00:20:41.220 --> 00:20:42.680
&gt;&gt; Dr. Michael Chorost: I think
[inaudible] end, you sort of hear

00:20:42.680 --> 00:20:44.900
that [makes sounds] kind
of sound, don't you?

