It could be that, right?

00:20:53.410 --> 00:20:55.120
All right, now eight channels.

00:20:55.120 --> 00:20:58.110
And when you hear this, you'll
hear a pretty good rendition

00:20:58.110 --> 00:21:03.590 position:56%
of what things sounded like to me on
that first day back in October 2001.

00:21:03.590 --> 00:21:08.340
I have to find a pointer.

