00:49:39.620 --> 00:49:41.780
You couldn't figure out the
auditory code of the ear.

00:49:41.780 --> 00:49:44.050
You couldn't surgically implant it.

00:49:44.050 --> 00:49:44.580
Forget it.

00:49:44.580 --> 00:49:45.760
That's nonsense.

00:49:45.760 --> 00:49:47.540
And yet indeed, it did happen.

